      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BETTY BULLPIT (7) has an honest record despite remaining a maiden after 13 starts. Was below best last time when missed the frame finishing sixth (43.98) at Wentworth Park. Good beginner but will need a little luck early crossing from an outside draw. Better than the latest effort and deserves another chance. HIGH CURRENT (1) collided with another runner and was out of the placings when a 10 length fifth (23.52) in a Maiden at this track. Can measure up this time. FEROCIOUS OUTLAW (4) delivered a moderate run last time when fifth at this track over 401m behind Indy's Shine (23.66). Will give the top chances plenty to think about. BOW MEYA (2) will give backers a sight.",
